\cf6 \
\pard\tx6480\pardeftab720\li576\ri-19445

\b0\fs28 \cf0 To the left of the target sequence is a column of numbers indicating the number of the base at the start of each row. If you resize the window or partition, these base numbers will change automatically to reflect the wrapping the sequence text.\
