\cf0 \
\pard\tx6480\pardeftab720\li576\ri-19445

\f2\fs28 \cf0 The search is case-insensitive and includes all three columns. You can find matches one at a time with the "Find Next" button, or select them all at once with "Select All." The latter is useful to select a related group of primers for copying, flipping, checking, etc.\
\
\pard\tx6480\pardeftab720\li270\ri-19445

